#

Classic Potato Draniki

$8.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Eggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

Comfort FoodEastern EuropeanFriedPancakes

Description

Crispy and golden potato pancakes, served with sour cream, bursting with flavor!

Ingredients

  • Potatoes: 4 medium
  • Onion: 1 medium
  • Egg: 1 large
  • Flour: 3 tablespoons
  • Salt: 1 teaspoon
  • Pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Oil for frying: as needed
  • Sour cream: for serving
